:::Cyclonus/Scourge/Starscream/Bludgeon/Obsidian:::

Scourge: Motormaster? The Stunticons are here?
::Then they see the thorougly bashed Stunticons walk in and hear their words::
Cyclonus: One would ask the same question to you, Speedbreaker.
Scourge: yeah, Cyclonus came here long before you, but was killed. For some 
unknown reason, hes back again. He found my stasis pod and the rest is 
history. Were here now, and want to join your group.
Cyclonus: I will serve Motormaster the same way i served Galvatron.
::They hear Switchblade::
Scourge: Seems were needed in the control room.
::They walk into the control room and look at Switchblade. They dont know who 
he is::
Cyclonus: So whats your name?
~~~~~
::My Predacons continue their assault on Hell Beast's base, although it 
seemed imposible to damage it::
